headline: GE Stock Jets To A New High. A Natural Gas Name Joins It.
summary: GE Aerospace stock has recovered from a sell-off and recently hit a new high.  Meanwhile, a natural gas name and McDonald's stock have also reached new levels.  All three are in buy zones with the earnings reports behind them.
